caption:
Jumpstart your career in management consulting by getting real-world experience solving problems with innovative startups and nonprofits from around the world!

As a Consulting Group Team Lead, you will have the opportunity to select and lead your team of talented UofT undergrad/grad students. We are looking for students with strong leadership skills interested in pursuing a career in consulting for this role. Applications are open to all UofT graduate students and upper-year undergraduates!

Applications close Sunday, August 25th 2024 at 11:59PM EST. Click the link in our bio to access the application form and learn more about UTCA’s Consulting Group Team Lead positions!

Looking for an opportunity to join a world renowned strategic consulting firm? Remember to join us 💫TONIGHT💫 from 7:00 - 8:30 pm to learn about internships and full-time opportunities at EY-Parthenon. Firm representatives will answer your questions about the recruitment timeline, corporate life and culture, interview preparation, and other valuable application tips and tricks. Don’t miss out! 🚀

🌟 Interested in a career in consulting? The Summer Firm Series, hosted by UTCA with representatives from top consulting firms, is an annual event series that connects industry leaders and emerging talent. Featuring panel discussions and networking sessions, attendees will learn more about the vast opportunities at top consulting firms from accomplished individuals. With spotlights on different consulting firms, this event is perfect for gaining knowledge regarding each individual firm and expanding your network. 

👨‍💼👩‍💼🧑‍💼 Join us for the opportunity to discover internships and full-time positions at EY Parthenon and meet talented consultants working at this world-renowned consulting firm. Our firm representatives will answer your questions about the recruitment timeline, corporate life and culture, interview preparation, and other valuable application tips and tricks. Don’t miss out!

🔗 Fill out the form (link in bio) to join our event with EY Parthenon on Aug 8th, 2024 at 7:00 - 8:30 pm. You will receive the Zoom link along with other details in your email prior to the event. 

The deadline to register is Aug 7th, 2024 at 11:59pm EST. ⚡️

We look forward to seeing you! 🎉

🤩 Curious about the cosmos? ASX’s got you covered— we’re UofT’s astronomy outreach club, bringing the wonders of the universe to you with free, open to the public events that are accessible to all! Come meet us at booth F31 and learn more about our out-of-this-world events at clubs fair! 

🗓️ 30th August, 1-4PM

📍King’s College Circle (front campus), Booth F31

#uoft #utsg #astronomy #astrophyiscs #universe #physics #space

🙋Drop by for a fun (and accessible) astro-themed trivia session at front campus, where you’ll even get to try out a solar telescope 🔭! Make sure to bring along your friends to secure a prize! 🏆

🗓️28th August, 2PM

📍King’s College Circle (grass patch, or adjacent areas if it’s still closed)

#uoft #utsg #astronomy #astrophyiscs #universe #physics #space #telescope

☀️ Summer is ending but we are back in full swing along with our observation nights! Experience the wonders of stargazing on McLennan’s rooftop observatory with us and @au.uoft, and the free snacks that we’ll be providing. We can’t wait to see you all! 🔭

🗓️30th August (day of clubs fair!), 9-11PM

📍McLennan Physical Laboratories (60 St. George Street)

#uoft #astronomy #astrophyiscs #universe #physics #space #telescope
